<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About The Village</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">The real estate in The Village is characterized by large townhouses and huge apartment complexes. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Security is of utmost importance to builders here and there are many well-guarded gated apartments that are up for sale. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Single-story condos are also available. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Further away from the center of the neighborhood many large bungalows and bi-level units with single attached garage are available for purchase. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Being a business area, there are many commercial centers, shopping complexes and business units that are located in and around the area. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">There are also parks, playgrounds, restaurants and cafes in the neighborhood.</p>
        </div>
